metadata.name: The tragedy of darkness
metadata.description:
How might your situation have been in a place where there's no happiness, no hope, no future, no consciousness?
How would you have felt in a place where no one can hear and understand you?
What would your thoughts have been in a place where everyone and everything wants shoot you down?
How would you have reacted in a place where you have no choice and no right as a human being?


acrylic on canvas, 40 x 60 cm
